WEBVTT

00:12.500 --> 00:14.500
Previously on  Ray Donovan...

00:14.583 --> 00:16.291
Try this one.
ABBY: You're a cop.

00:16.375 --> 00:17.917
Well, you never know when
you're gonna get in trouble.

00:18.000 --> 00:19.458
If you do, give me a call.

00:19.542 --> 00:20.166
We met today at the gun range.

00:20.250 --> 00:22.417
I'm going back there tomorrow.

00:25.458 --> 00:28.041
MICKEY: What'd your father say
about what happened?

00:28.125 --> 00:29.667
He was supposed to take me
to the kid's house to apologize.

00:29.750 --> 00:32.166
Donovans don't apologize.

00:32.250 --> 00:33.375
RE-KON:
It's your new birthday, son.

00:33.458 --> 00:35.250
You got a whole new life
ahead of you.

00:35.333 --> 00:36.458
Thanks, Re-Kon.

00:36.542 --> 00:37.792
BRIDGET: Jesus, Marvin,
what are you doing here?

00:37.875 --> 00:38.917
My dad will kill you.

00:39.000 --> 00:40.208
I miss you, Bridg.

00:40.291 --> 00:41.750
I've gone to some very bad
places in my life

00:41.834 --> 00:43.917
trying to be brave.

00:44.000 --> 00:45.083
So have I.

00:45.166 --> 00:46.750
LINDA:
So we have that in common.

00:46.834 --> 00:48.583
MICKEY: It's not the way
things are done, Sully.

00:48.667 --> 00:50.125
You kill a woman
for passion.

00:50.208 --> 00:51.834
This is business.
(gunshot)

00:51.917 --> 00:52.709
DEB:
This is Abby Donovan.

00:52.792 --> 00:55.458
Maybe your new neighbor.

00:55.542 --> 00:57.709
Oh, you're from Boston.

00:57.792 --> 00:59.500
I find it charming.

00:59.583 --> 01:00.917
Why are you talking like that?

01:01.000 --> 01:02.667
(flat American accent):
Whatever do you mean?

01:02.750 --> 01:04.458
(moaning)
KATE: Just because we fucked

01:04.542 --> 01:06.000
doesn't mean I won't do my job.

01:06.083 --> 01:07.500
Can I see you again?

01:07.583 --> 01:08.542
COCHRAN:
This asshole was fucking

01:08.625 --> 01:10.083
mouthing off to a detective.

01:10.166 --> 01:11.917
Said he was on the docks
the night that Sully got shot.

01:12.000 --> 01:14.166
Don't kill him.
COCHRAN: Who said anything
about killing anybody?

01:14.250 --> 01:15.375
(gunshot)

01:15.458 --> 01:16.125
(groans)

01:16.208 --> 01:18.917
Kate McPherson, Boston Globe.

01:19.000 --> 01:20.667
I got a story for you.

01:20.750 --> 01:22.041
I'll need to speak
with you in person.

01:22.125 --> 01:23.083
Can you meet me?
RAY: You talk to my father,

01:23.166 --> 01:24.625
your life is in danger.

01:24.709 --> 01:26.125
I'm texting you an address.

01:26.208 --> 01:26.709
Will you be there?

01:26.792 --> 01:28.667
MAN:
Mickey Donovan!

01:28.750 --> 01:30.458
(grunting)

01:38.458 --> 01:40.291
♪ ♪

01:42.875 --> 01:45.125
♪ I found God in ♪

01:45.208 --> 01:47.417
♪ The embrace of your arms ♪

01:47.500 --> 01:52.959
♪ Little did I know that you
would put me in harm's way ♪

01:53.041 --> 01:54.500
(dogs snarling)

01:54.583 --> 01:59.208
