you down the stairs.

02:37.291 --> 02:39.667
But you did break my phone.

02:46.000 --> 02:46.583
(scoffs)

02:46.667 --> 02:48.917
Is that it?

02:49.000 --> 02:50.208
Go on.

02:50.291 --> 02:51.208
Go on, what? I said I
shouldn't have done it.

02:51.291 --> 02:55.834
I didn't hear the words,
"I'm sorry."

02:56.959 --> 03:00.291
Tell him you're sorry.

03:00.375 --> 03:02.291
Dad, it's okay. We're friends.
Hey.

03:03.458 --> 03:05.041
Is he gonna apologize or not?

03:06.375 --> 03:06.667
Conor.

03:06.750 --> 03:08.834
What?

03:08.917 --> 03:10.875
Say you're sorry.

03:10.959 --> 03:12.792
He shouldn't make me a bitch.

03:12.875 --> 03:14.125
Hey.
A bitch?

03:14.208 --> 03:16.458
Is this what you teach him?
You don't talk

03:16.542 --> 03:17.750
to us like that.
Relax.

03:17.834 --> 03:18.750
Look at me when I'm talking,

03:18.834 --> 03:19.583
you little dick.
This is over.

03:19.667 --> 03:21.959
Over?

03:22.041 --> 03:23.250
Come on, Con, let's go.

03:23.333 --> 03:26.583
He broke my kid's collarbone,
for Christ's sake.

03:26.667 --> 03:28.583
He's a menace!

03:28.667 --> 03:30.625
You're gonna hear
from my lawyer!

03:47.917 --> 03:49.208
(sighs)

03:55.625 --> 03:57.458
(exhales)

04:00.166 --> 04:02.375
You blocked me in
at the boxing gym.

04:03.875 --> 04:05.875
Ray sent me to watch you.

04:05.959 --> 04:07.375
