04:11.667 --> 04:14.125
Ray told me to show you this.

04:16.208 --> 04:18.208
You know who that is, right?

04:18.291 --> 04:19.375
Kenneth Benson.

04:19.458 --> 04:22.041
Tiny. He was part
of Sully's gang.

04:22.125 --> 04:23.083
Ray was not kidding.

04:23.166 --> 04:24.834
Things are dangerous now.

04:26.083 --> 04:28.125
I can take care of myself.

04:28.709 --> 04:31.625
(sighs)

04:39.000 --> 04:40.458
(phone rings)

04:42.333 --> 04:43.709
(chirps)
Yeah?

04:43.792 --> 04:46.000
