last night.

04:46.083 --> 04:48.000
What do you mean, "took him"?

04:48.083 --> 04:48.792
Took him.

04:48.875 --> 04:51.458
They kidnapped him!

04:51.542 --> 04:53.041
They broke the
fucking door down!

04:53.125 --> 04:54.208
Those guys were pros!

04:54.291 --> 04:55.417
Hey, shut up.
Big time!

04:55.500 --> 04:56.875
Sit the fuck down.
Someone took Grandpa?

04:56.959 --> 04:57.792
Find him.

04:57.875 --> 04:59.959
Do your job.

05:00.041 --> 05:02.208
(sighs) What the fuck
do you think I'm doing?

05:02.291 --> 05:04.417
(softly):
Piece of sh...

05:04.500 --> 05:06.000
(sighs)

05:06.083 --> 05:07.125
