05:07.208 --> 05:08.375
That was his parole officer.

05:08.458 --> 05:09.542
He'll find him.

05:11.208 --> 05:12.542
Dad?

05:12.625 --> 05:14.834
Did he really kill somebody?

05:17.333 --> 05:20.041
I don't want
to talk about it, Con.

05:20.125 --> 05:23.083
It was a long time ago.

05:27.208 --> 05:30.041
Oh, I heard from
Senator Feinstein's office.

05:30.125 --> 05:33.792
We are set for the
fund-raiser tonight.

05:33.875 --> 05:36.000
Head table.

05:37.500 --> 05:39.250
