05:39.333 --> 05:41.583
Oh, sweetie, look
at those scratches.

05:41.667 --> 05:44.417
Let me get you some Neosporin.

05:48.083 --> 05:49.709
You were a real
tiger last night.

05:49.792 --> 05:51.542
Never seen you
like that before.

05:53.667 --> 05:55.166
Ed, what's wrong?

05:55.250 --> 05:56.500
Loose ends. I just...

05:56.583 --> 05:57.917
I'm cleaning
them up today, though.

05:58.000 --> 06:00.542
That is right, babe.

06:00.625 --> 06:03.250
You don't let anything
distract you.

06:03.333 --> 06:07.125
You have to be on point tonight
with Senator Feinstein.

06:07.208 --> 06:08.542
She's a gun-hating liberal.

06:11.333 --> 06:14.000
She is the senior member
of the judiciary committee,

06:14.083 --> 06:15.917
and we are going
to need her support

06:16.041 --> 06:16.875
for your confirmation.

06:16.959 --> 06:18.083
Yeah.

06:18.166 --> 06:21.792
Eddie, keep your eyes

06:21.875 --> 06:23.792
on the prize.

06:23.875 --> 06:24.375
You're right.

06:24.458 --> 06:27.125
You're right, as usual.

06:27.208 --> 06:29.834
(laughing):
Hey, hey.

06:33.875 --> 06:35.750
Hey, Frank.

06:35.834 --> 06:38.959
Oh, fuck!

06:40.083 --> 06:41.000
Where's my father?

06:41.083 --> 06:43.083
I don't know!

06:43.166 --> 06:45.458
(grunts)
Your guys took him.

06:45.542 --> 06:46.333
Where'd you put him?
I don't know

06:46.417 --> 06:48.792
and I don't give a shit.
Yeah?

06:48.875 --> 06:49.625
(groaning)

06:51.333 --> 06:53.250
Oh! Fuck!

06:54.166 --> 06:56.000
(groans)

06:58.208 --> 06:59.583
Where is he, Frank?

06:59.667 --> 07:01.291
You think Cochran
tells me anything?

07:01.375 --> 07:02.792
He doesn't tell me shit.

07:02.875 --> 07:03.959
He tells you to kill people.

07:04.041 --> 07:05.583
He made me kill
that poor fat fucker.

07:05.667 --> 07:07.041
It was like killing
a fucking dog.

07:07.125 --> 07:08.709
Oh, fuck!

07:08.792 --> 07:10.000
Where's my father, Frank?

07:10.083 --> 07:11.583
I don't know!
Cochran's cut me out!

07:11.667 --> 07:13.750
Then give me something
I can use against him.

07:13.834 --> 07:16.000
I think he's clean.

07:16.083 --> 07:18.417
All right, all right! Fuck!

07:19.917 --> 07:21.542
