(panting)

07:23.333 --> 07:25.208
His ASAC, Volcheck.

07:25.959 --> 07:28.166
Fuck.

07:28.250 --> 07:30.583
(grunting)

07:30.667 --> 07:31.792
Fuck!

07:31.875 --> 07:33.208
That was for Tiny.

07:34.792 --> 07:35.500
(beeping)

07:35.583 --> 07:38.834
BRIDGET:
Mama, I'm getting sick.

07:38.917 --> 07:40.875
I think I should stay
home from school.

07:40.959 --> 07:42.500
Okay.

07:42.583 --> 07:43.625
Okay?

07:46.542 --> 07:47.083
What's that?

07:47.166 --> 07:49.709
It's a gun.

07:49.792 --> 07:51.667
Your father gave it to me.

07:51.750 --> 07:53.166
What's it for?

07:53.250 --> 07:56.041
I shoot it at a range.

07:56.125 --> 07:58.000
It's a sport.

07:58.083 --> 07:59.709
I really think I'm sick.

07:59.792 --> 08:01.625
Feel my head.

08:02.166 --> 08:04.625
Oh, it feels fine.

08:04.709 --> 08:06.291
You barely touched it.

08:06.375 --> 08:08.959
Do you want to see a doctor?

08:09.041 --> 08:10.333
No, but...

08:11.875 --> 08:13.125
So stay home.

08:13.208 --> 08:15.125
You're making straight A's.

08:17.166 --> 08:20.125
Don't you want to
check my temperature?

08:20.208 --> 08:22.208
There's a thermometer
in the bathroom.

08:25.291 --> 08:27.375
(chuckles)

08:50.458 --> 08:52.583
Mickey disappeared last night.

08:53.875 --> 08:54.959
Call Steve Davis.

08:55.041 --> 08:55.917
See if he knows anything.

08:56.000 --> 08:57.166
Okay, boss.

08:57.250 --> 08:58.959
You want me to check
the morgue, too?

08:59.041 --> 08:59.667
No, not yet.

09:01.500 --> 09:02.750
Yeah, Officer Steve Davis?

09:14.291 --> 09:16.458
Look at the time.

09:16.542 --> 09:17.583
What about it?

09:17.667 --> 09:19.709
Director of the Los Angeles FBI

09:19.792 --> 09:23.375
socializing with his ASAC
until 2:00 in the morning.

09:23.458 --> 09:24.959
Cochran's supposed
to be fucking her.

09:25.041 --> 09:26.291
