09:26.375 --> 09:27.625
Okay.

09:48.250 --> 09:51.542
Excuse me, can you tell me where
Frank Barnes keeps his boat?

09:59.041 --> 10:01.041
Special Agent Barnes.

10:01.125 --> 10:04.333
I've been trying to talk to
you for the past few days.

10:04.417 --> 10:06.458
I'm a reporter for
The Boston Globe,

10:06.542 --> 10:08.208
and for some reason, your
boss won't let me near you.

10:08.291 --> 10:10.458
You want to tell me why?

10:10.542 --> 10:11.959
(sighs)

10:12.041 --> 10:13.166
No comment.

10:17.834 --> 10:19.542
Nobody could catch Sully,

10:19.625 --> 10:20.709
but you did.
You ought to get

10:20.792 --> 10:23.375
