not just a medal.

10:25.875 --> 10:27.750
Leave me alone.

10:27.834 --> 10:29.333
What happened to your face?

10:31.792 --> 10:33.417
I know your boss is lying.

10:33.500 --> 10:36.208
Sully didn't arrive in
L.A. when he said he did.

10:36.291 --> 10:38.500
I also know that Mickey Donovan
was on the docks

10:38.583 --> 10:40.834
the night Sully was killed.

10:40.917 --> 10:43.250
Maybe the FBI didn't have
a plan to catch Sully.

10:43.333 --> 10:45.542
Maybe they just got lucky.

10:45.625 --> 10:47.750
Come on, Frank.

10:47.834 --> 10:48.583
What is Cochran hiding?

10:48.667 --> 10:51.750
You're gonna get
yourself killed.

10:53.291 --> 10:53.792
What did you just say?

10:58.333 --> 11:00.250
Nothing.

11:07.125 --> 11:08.458
Frank!

11:08.542 --> 11:11.417
Why would someone want
to kill me?

11:11.500 --> 11:13.417
Who beat you up, Frank?

11:13.500 --> 11:14.875
Ask your fucking boyfriend.

11:14.959 --> 11:17.291
Are you talking
about Ray Donovan?

11:17.375 --> 11:19.458
(panting)

11:35.834 --> 11:38.500
(engine starts)

11:45.250 --> 11:48.125
(phone ringing)

11:52.625 --> 11:53.250
Yeah?

11:53.333 --> 11:55.875
She ditched me.

11:55.959 --> 11:56.875
I lost her.

11:56.959 --> 11:57.625
Damn it, Av.
What can I do?

11:57.709 --> 11:59.792
She jumped on a fucking boat!

12:01.875 --> 12:04.792
(phone rings)

12:04.875 --> 12:05.458
Conor?

12:05.542 --> 12:07.709
Dad? Did you find Grandpa?

12:07.792 --> 12:09.083
He's gonna be fine, Con.

12:09.166 --> 12:10.208
How do you know?

12:11.709 --> 12:13.333
There's no one out there
who wants to hurt him.

12:13.417 --> 12:14.834
You did!
I did what?

12:14.917 --> 12:15.625
You pistol-whipped him,
remember?

12:15.709 --> 12:17.583
Yeah, well, that was different.

12:17.667 --> 12:19.792
Are you really looking for him?

12:19.875 --> 12:22.834
Conor, your grandfather's
gonna be fine.

12:36.917 --> 12:38.000
(grunting)

12:52.000 --> 12:53.542
You like it? You like it?!

12:53.625 --> 12:54.792
Put me in a fucking cage!

12:54.875 --> 12:55.917
You think you can scare me?!

12:56.000 --> 12:59.417
Fuck you! Fuck you! Fuck you!

12:59.500 --> 13:01.583
(gunfire)

13:31.125 --> 13:33.375
Are those real diamonds?

13:33.458 --> 13:34.750
(laughs)

13:34.834 --> 13:36.000
Of course they real, Shawty.

13:40.792 --> 13:43.458
You know, I don't need
both of these.

13:45.125 --> 13:46.041
Really?

13:46.125 --> 13:47.166
Come here.

13:48.542 --> 13:52.250
Take that one out.

13:59.208 --> 14:01.083
(quiet laugh)

14:01.166 --> 14:03.917
You wear one
and I wear one.

14:04.000 --> 14:05.875
What's this for?

14:05.959 --> 14:07.083
'Cause you're mine.

14:10.625 --> 14:11.125
I love it!

14:13.458 --> 14:15.542
Thank you.

14:18.375 --> 14:20.375
(phone chimes)

14:20.458 --> 14:22.542
Sorry.

14:25.250 --> 14:27.166
You want to go to a party?

14:56.959 --> 14:58.291
SHORTY:
What the fuck are you doing?

14:58.375 --> 15:00.917
I'm looking for
Mickey Donovan.

15:01.000 --> 15:01.917
What for?

15:02.000 --> 15:02.959
I'm a reporter.

15:03.041 --> 15:05.333
Oh, he was waiting
for you last night!

15:05.417 --> 15:06.375
Oh, he had
some important shit

15:06.458 --> 15:08.709
to tell you.

15:08.792 --> 15:09.834
Da Vinci Code-type  shit.

15:09.917 --> 15:13.583
Now, I don't know
where he's at.

15:13.667 --> 15:15.750
Maybe the Vatican.

15:15.834 --> 15:17.709
They're probably torturing him.

15:17.792 --> 15:20.834
He wanted to give you this.

15:23.083 --> 15:25.792
Well, I'll be on my way.

15:35.417 --> 15:37.000
You need to go back to Boston.

15:37.083 --> 15:39.542
Is this how you
get rid of girls?

15:39.625 --> 15:40.875
You're causing
a lot of headaches

15:40.959 --> 15:42.166
for some very dangerous people.

15:42.250 --> 15:43.166
I'm trying to protect you.

15:43.250 --> 15:46.208
When I was writing
about pedophile priests,

15:46.291 --> 15:48.625
I got death threats
all the time.

15:48.709 --> 15:50.417
That didn't stop me.

15:50.500 --> 15:52.625
Sully didn't die

15:52.709 --> 15:54.333
the way the FBI said he did.

15:54.417 --> 15:55.333
I can't finish

15:55.417 --> 15:57.500
my book until I know
what really happened.

15:59.709 --> 16:02.041
It really bothers
you, doesn't it?

16:02.125 --> 16:04.208
Not being in control?

16:16.875 --> 16:18.333
(cell phone ringing)

16:23.875 --> 16:24.709
Yeah?

16:24.792 --> 16:27.083
I know where he is.

16:27.166 --> 16:28.709
Where?

16:28.792 --> 16:29.792
It's gonna cost you.

16:29.875 --> 16:31.208
Are you fucking kidding me?

16:31.291 --> 16:34.208
Everything I'm doing
for you is illegal.

16:34.291 --> 16:36.208
I could lose my fucking job.

16:36.291 --> 16:37.709
What do you want?

16:38.917 --> 16:42.166
I was at the track yesterday.

16:42.250 --> 16:44.709
And I'm down.

16:44.792 --> 16:46.041
Seven grand?

16:47.875 --> 16:50.709
Go to my office.
The girl will give it to you.

16:50.792 --> 16:52.333
Now, where the fuck
is my father?

16:59.375 --> 17:01.458
(door closes)

17:04.375 --> 17:06.208
It's you.

17:08.542 --> 17:10.041
