a shit about you? Ray?

17:14.834 --> 17:17.750
For one.
Oh, yeah?

17:17.834 --> 17:20.000
Paid Sully $2 million
to have you killed.

17:20.083 --> 17:23.083
Eh, it's a complicated
relationship.

17:23.166 --> 17:24.959
Maybe you want to call

17:25.041 --> 17:26.333
that fucking reporter.

17:26.417 --> 17:28.875
Oh!

17:28.959 --> 17:30.083
You're spying on me!

17:30.166 --> 17:32.625
That's against the law.
That's against the law.

17:32.709 --> 17:33.709
There's no law here, Mick.
There's just me.

17:33.792 --> 17:36.750
I'm the law! Me!

17:36.834 --> 17:37.792
I'm about

17:37.875 --> 17:40.041
to become the number one
law enforcement officer

17:40.125 --> 17:43.834
in the United States, hell, in
the fucking free world, Mick!

17:43.917 --> 17:45.750
But you Irish Spring,
you Lucky Charms-eating

17:45.834 --> 17:47.417
pieces of fucking shit!

17:47.500 --> 17:49.333
You guys are gonna
bring me down.

17:49.417 --> 17:51.625
Top of the morning to you.

17:51.709 --> 17:52.750
You know, Mick,

17:52.834 --> 17:55.834
I have this ambition.

17:55.917 --> 17:57.875
I don't know where
it comes from.

17:57.959 --> 18:00.166
My whole life I've
been on this path

18:00.250 --> 18:02.792
towards greatness.

18:02.875 --> 18:04.125
I'm disciplined, too.

18:04.208 --> 18:05.166
I don't lie.

18:05.250 --> 18:06.709
I don't cheat on my taxes.

18:06.792 --> 18:08.041
I don't text when I drive.

18:08.125 --> 18:09.709
Regular Boy Scout.

18:13.208 --> 18:15.500
Why does Ray hate you so much?

18:15.583 --> 18:17.125
I wish I could tell you.

18:17.208 --> 18:18.291
You must've done
something to the guy.

18:18.375 --> 18:19.500
